{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"1. Bij de winden, die na elkaar vooruit zijn gestuurd.","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:2","price":"2. En bij de winden die hard blazen.","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:3","price":"3. En bij de winden die de wolken en regen verspreiden,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:4","price":"4. En bij de verzen die het goede van het foute scheiden.","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:5","price":"5. En bij de engelen die de openbaringen naar de boodschappers brengen.","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:6","price":"6. Als een excuus en als een waarschuwing.","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:7","price":"7. Waarlijk, wat jullie beloofd is zal vervuld worden.","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:8","price":"8. Als dan de sterren hun licht verliezen","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:9","price":"9. En de hemel splijt.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:10","price":"10. En de bergen weggeblazen worden.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:11","price":"11. En als de boodschappers verzameld worden op de hen aangewezen tijd.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:12","price":"12. Voor welke dag is het uitgesteld?","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:13","price":"13. Voor de dag van de beslissing.","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:14","price":"14. En wat zal jullie weten wat de dag van de beslissing is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:15","price":"15. Wee die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:16","price":"16. Hebben wij de eerdere generaties niet vernietigd?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:17","price":"17. Zo zullen Wij latere generaties hen laten volgen.","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:18","price":"18. Zo gaan Wij met de misdadigers om.","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:19","price":"19. Wee op die dag de ontkenners.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:20","price":"20. Hebben Wij jullie niet uit een zwak vloeistof geschapen?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:21","price":"21. Toen hebben Wij jullie in een veilige plaats gezet (in de baarmoeder).","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ فِي قَرَارٖ مَّكِينٍ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5643,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:22","price":"22. Voor een bekende periode.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5644,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:23","price":"23. Zo hebben Wij het bepaald en Wij zijn de beste om (zaken) te bepalen.","arabic":"فَقَدَرۡنَا فَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5645,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:24","price":"24. Wee op die dag de ontkenners.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5646,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:25","price":"25. Hebben Wij de aarde niet als een verzamelplaats gemaakt.","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ كِفَاتًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5647,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:26","price":"26. Voor de levenden en de doden.","arabic":"أَحۡيَآءٗ وَأَمۡوَٰتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5648,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:27","price":"27. En daarin ferme en hoge bergen geplaatst en jullie zoet water te drinken gegeven?","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِيَ شَٰمِخَٰتٖ وَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰكُم مَّآءٗ فُرَاتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5649,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:28","price":"28. Wee op die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5650,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:29","price":"29. (Er zal gezegd worden tegen de ongelovigen:) \"Vertrek jullie naar datgene wat jullie plachten te ontkennen!”","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5651,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:30","price":"30. Vertrek jullie naar een schaduw in drie kolommen.","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ ظِلّٖ ذِي ثَلَٰثِ شُعَبٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5652,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:31","price":"31. De schaduw kan niet van enig nut zijn tegen de felle vlammen van het vuur.","arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٖ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5653,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:32","price":"32. Waarlijk! Het (de hel) werpt vonken uit (groot) als een fort of een groot blok hout.","arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرۡمِي بِشَرَرٖ كَٱلۡقَصۡرِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5654,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:33","price":"33. Alsof zij gele kamelen waren.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَٰلَتٞ صُفۡرٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5655,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:34","price":"34. Wee op die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5656,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:35","price":"35. Dat zal een dag zijn wanneer zij niet zullen spreken.","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5657,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:36","price":"36. En het zal hun niet toegestaan worden om zich te verontschuldigen.","arabic":"وَلَا يُؤۡذَنُ لَهُمۡ فَيَعۡتَذِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5658,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:37","price":"37. Wee op die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5659,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:38","price":"38. Dat zal de dag zijn van het besluit! Wij hebben jullie en de eerdere generaties tezamen gebracht!","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِۖ جَمَعۡنَٰكُمۡ وَٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5660,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:39","price":"39. Als jullie een samenzwering hebben gebruik hem dan (tegen Mij)!","arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمۡ كَيۡدٞ فَكِيدُونِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5661,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:40","price":"40. Wee op die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5662,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:41","price":"41. Waarlijk de godvrezenden zullen temidden van schaduw en bronnen zijn.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي ظِلَٰلٖ وَعُيُونٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5663,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:42","price":"42. En fruit – zoals zij wensen.","arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5664,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:43","price":"43. “Eet en drink in alle gemak vanwege wat jullie plachten te doen.”","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5665,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:44","price":"44. Waarlijk, zo belonen Wij de weldoeners.","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5666,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:45","price":"45. Wee op die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5667,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:46","price":"46. Eet en vermaak jezelf voor korte tijd. Waarlijk jullie zijn de misdadigers.","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَتَمَتَّعُواْ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجۡرِمُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5668,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:47","price":"47. Wee op die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5669,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:48","price":"48. En als er tegen hen gezegd wordt: “Buig, dan Buigen zij niet neer.\"","arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرۡكَعُواْ لَا يَرۡكَعُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5670,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:49","price":"49. Wee op die dag de ontkenners!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5671,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"77:50","price":"50. In welke boodschap hierna zullen zij dan wel geloven?","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثِۭ بَعۡدَهُۥ يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5672,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"}],"chapter":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat","Chapter Al-Mursalat","Mursalat","Surah Mursalat","Chapter Mursalat","Al Mursalat","Surah Al Mursalat","Chapter Al Mursalat","Surah 77","Chapter 77","The Emissaries","المرسلات"]}